column5: A quick question for anyone who can help me out...while moving I misplaced my boat registration.  Where do I get a new one?  A friend told me to go to the DMV?  Some trying to save a head ache!!! Thanks in advance.
DMV can't help you... Services Canada looks after it now instead of Canada Customs.
Thanks!!  Looked it up and I have what I need.  Again thanks!!
